      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"3. LULU'S DREAM is better than last start when sixth (30.46) in a Class 5 H at this track over 520m. Has a good record here at this journey. Two runs back from a brief spell should see her nearing peak fitness. Has ability and looks hard to stop. 2. CRIMINAL MINDS was out of the placings last time when eighth at this track (32.02) but did record best time of the card when winning three back. Has a strong record out of this box with five wins and a minor placing from nine starts. Likely to be about the mark. 5. SUPER LEAGUE was out of the placings last time but shapes well for this on his lightning win the start prior, getting around Manawatu over 457m in 25.12. Top win two back and rates a key player again. 4. LET HIM COOK did have a solo trial (17.05) at Addington over 295m then came here and ran a stylish third over 520m. Can feature in the finish today.\",\"runners\":[3,2,5,4],\"exclusive\":false}",
